      "message": "I thought about this more last night. I think that we\u0027d be better served by splitting this into two fields:\n  * step_class (string) - A \"what is this?\" identifier for a step, to be filled by a human to identify a step (or autogenerated by monitor\u003dTrue in the recipe engine). This will be included in BQ rows.\n  * monitor (bool) - Tell the system (kitchen/etc.) to export timeseries data for this step.\n\nThen we can eventually decouple these in the recipe engine too (allowing step_class to be set independently of having monitoring for a step).\n\nWDYT?",
